#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:264
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Accounts List can be filtered in two ways. Checking the \"Hide unused "
#| "categories\" checkbox hides any Categories for which no value has been "
#| "assigned to the Category or any of its Subcategories. To the right of "
#| "this, is an unlabelled text box. Only categories which include whatever "
#| "is typed in this box are listed, but their parent categories are also "
#| "listed."
msgid ""
"The Categories List can be filtered in two ways. Checking the <guilabel>Hide "
"unused budget categories</guilabel> checkbox hides any Categories for which "
"no value has been assigned to the Category or any of its Subcategories in "
"the selected budget. To the right of this, is an unlabelled text box. Only "
"categories which include whatever is typed in this box are listed, but their "
"parent categories are also listed."
msgstr ""
"Kontode nimekirja saab filtreerida kahel viisil. Kui märkida kastike "
"\"Kasutamata kategooriate peitmine\", peidetakse kõik kategooriad, mille "
"puhul pole ei kategooriale ega ühelegi selle alamkategooriale väärtust "
"omistatud. Sellest paremal asub pealdiseta tekstikast. Kui sinna midagi "
"kirjutada, näidatakse ainult kategooriaid, mis vastavad kirjutatule, aga "
"siiski ka nende ülemkategooriaid."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:273
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note that changing either the \"Hide unused budget categories\" or the "
#| "filter value is likely to change the list of Categories display. You may "
#| "need to re-expand the list to see all the Categories that should be "
#| "displayed with the current settings."
msgid ""
"Note that changing either the <guilabel>Hide unused budget categories</"
"guilabel> or the filter value is likely to change the list of Categories "
"displayed. You may need to re-expand the list to see all the Categories that "
"should be displayed with the current settings."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et nii kastikese \"Kasutamata eelarvekategooriate peitmine\" "
"märkimine kui ka väärtuste filtreerimine muudab usutavasti kategooriate "
"vaadet. Võib tekkida vajadus nimekiri uuesti lahti kerida, et näha kõiki "
"kategooriaid, mida kehtivate seadistuste alusel peaks nägema."

