#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update and Revert"
msgstr "Uuendamine ja lähtestamine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:393
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When a Budget's values are first modified, the Update and Revert buttons "
#| "are enabled. Multiple changes can be made to the Budget. Pressing Update "
#| "will store the changes and disable the Update and Revert buttons."
msgid ""
"When a Budget's values are first modified, the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons are enabled. Multiple changes can "
"be made to the Budget. Pressing <guibutton>Update</guibutton> will store the "
"changes and disable these buttons."
msgstr ""
"Eelarve väärtuste muutmisel, muutuvad aktiivseks ka uuendamis- ja "
"lähtestamisnupp. Eelarvesse võib teha mitmeid muutusi. Uuendamisnupule "
"klõpsamine salvestab muudatused ning muudab uuendamis- ja lähtestamisnupu "
"taas mitteaktiivseks."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:400
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kappname; Save only saves changes that have been stored using the "
#| "Update button. Thus, if you have modified a Budget but not yet stored the "
#| "changes &kappname; Save will not affect the modified Budget and the "
#| "Update and Revert buttons remain enabled."
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button only saves changes that have been "
"stored using the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> button. Thus, if you have "
"modified a Budget but not yet stored the changes <guibutton>Save</guibutton> "
"button will not affect the modified Budget and the <guibutton>Update</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons remain enabled."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; üldine salvestamine salvestab ainult muudatused, mis on "
"salvestatud uuendamisnupu abil. Niisiis, kui oled eelarvet muutnud, aga ei "
"ole veel uuendamisnupule klõpsanud, siis ei mõjuta &kappname; üldine "
"salvestamine muudetud eelarvet ning ka uuendamis- ja lähtestamisnupp on "
"jätkuvalt aktiivsed."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:408
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Revert undoes any changes made to a Budget since the last Update and "
#| "disables the Update and Revert buttons."
msgid ""
"Revert undoes any changes made to a Budget since the last Update and "
"disables the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"Lähtestamine tühistab kõik muudatused, mida oled eelarvesse teinud pärast "
"viimast uuendamist, ning muudab uuendamis. ja lähtestamisnupu "
"mitteaktiivseks."

